#: ../../communications.rst:67
msgid ""
"Some interesting options to *dig* are ``         +time=N        `` for "
"setting a query timeout to ``                   N                 `` "
"seconds, ``         +nofail        `` for continuing to query servers until "
"a reply is received, and ``         -x        `` for doing a reverse address"
" lookup."
